<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>CoE Portfolio · Overview</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=SF+Pro+Display:wght@200;300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
<style>
  :root {
    /* Apple-inspired palette: deep, quiet, with intention */
    --bg: #000000;
    --bg-elev-1: #0a0a0c;
    --bg-elev-2: #131316;
    --bg-elev-3: #1c1c20;
    --surface: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
    --surface-hover: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    --border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    --border-strong: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);

    --text: #f5f5f7;
    --text-secondary: rgba(245, 245, 247, 0.72);
    --text-tertiary: rgba(245, 245, 247, 0.48);
    --text-quaternary: rgba(245, 245, 247, 0.28);

    /* Accents — used sparingly, like punctuation */
    --blue: #0a84ff;
    --indigo: #5e5ce6;
    --purple: #bf5af2;
    --pink: #ff375f;
    --red: #ff453a;
    --orange: #ff9f0a;
    --yellow: #ffd60a;
    --green: #30d158;
    --mint: #63e6e2;
    --cyan: #64d2ff;
    --teal: #40c8e0;

    --font: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "SF Pro Display", "SF Pro Text", system-ui, sans-serif;

    /* Type scale — Apple-esque proportions */
    --text-xs: 11px;
    --text-sm: 12px;
    --text-base: 14px;
    --text-md: 15px;
    --text-lg: 17px;
    --text-xl: 22px;
    --text-2xl: 28px;
    --text-3xl: 40px;
    --text-4xl: 56px;
    --text-5xl: 72px;
    --text-hero: 96px;

    /* Spacing */
    --space-1: 4px;
    --space-2: 8px;
    --space-3: 12px;
    --space-4: 16px;
    --space-5: 20px;
    --space-6: 24px;
    --space-8: 32px;
    --space-10: 40px;
    --space-12: 48px;
    --space-16: 64px;
    --space-20: 80px;
    --space-24: 96px;

    --radius-sm: 8px;
    --radius-md: 12px;
    --radius-lg: 18px;
    --radius-xl: 24px;
    --radius-2xl: 32px;

    --ease: cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.1, 0.25, 1);
    --ease-spring: cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1);

    /* Dark-mode-specific layered images (used in body & hero-block) */
    --body-bg-image:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 50% at 50% -10%, rgba(94, 92, 230, 0.12), transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 40% at 80% 50%, rgba(10, 132, 255, 0.06), transparent 50%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 40% at 20% 90%, rgba(191, 90, 242, 0.05), transparent 50%);
    --hero-block-bg:
      radial-gradient(ellipse at top right, rgba(191, 90, 242, 0.2), transparent 50%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse at bottom left, rgba(10, 132, 255, 0.15), transparent 50%),
      linear-gradient(135deg, #0a0a12 0%, #14141f 100%);
    --hero-title-gradient: linear-gradient(180deg, #fff 0%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6) 100%);
    --kpi-hero-value-gradient: linear-gradient(180deg, #fff 0%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7) 100%);
    --banner-bg: rgba(10, 10, 12, 0.85);
    --grain-opacity: 0.015;
    --grain-blend: overlay;
  }

  /* ——————————————————————— LIGHT MODE ——————————————————————— */
  [data-theme="light"] {
    --bg: #fbfbfd;
    --bg-elev-1: #f5f5f7;
    --bg-elev-2: #ffffff;
    --bg-elev-3: #ffffff;
    --surface: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.025);
    --surface-hover: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.045);
    --border: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    --border-strong: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.14);

    --text: #1d1d1f;
    --text-secondary: rgba(29, 29, 31, 0.72);
    --text-tertiary: rgba(29, 29, 31, 0.52);
    --text-quaternary: rgba(29, 29, 31, 0.32);

    /* Accents shift slightly darker for AA contrast on light bg */
    --blue: #0066cc;
    --indigo: #5048e5;
    --purple: #a339d9;
    --pink: #e11d48;
    --red: #d70015;
    --orange: #c93400;
    --yellow: #a16207;
    --green: #28a745;
    --mint: #0d9488;
    --cyan: #0891b2;
    --teal: #0e7490;

    --body-bg-image:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 50% at 50% -10%, rgba(80, 72, 229, 0.08), transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 40% at 80% 50%, rgba(0, 102, 204, 0.05), transparent 50%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 40% at 20% 90%, rgba(163, 57, 217, 0.04), transparent 50%);
    --hero-block-bg:
      radial-gradient(ellipse at top right, rgba(163, 57, 217, 0.12), transparent 50%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse at bottom left, rgba(0, 102, 204, 0.08), transparent 50%),
      linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 0%, #f5f5f7 100%);
    --hero-title-gradient: linear-gradient(180deg, #1d1d1f 0%, rgba(29, 29, 31, 0.65) 100%);
    --kpi-hero-value-gradient: linear-gradient(180deg, #1d1d1f 0%, rgba(29, 29, 31, 0.7) 100%);
    --banner-bg: rgba(251, 251, 253, 0.85);
    --grain-opacity: 0.008;
    --grain-blend: multiply;
  }

  /* Smooth theme transitions on themable properties */
  html, body, .card, .worktype, .outcome, .timeline-card, .person-card,
  .kpi-hero, .pipeline-card, .hero-block, .recs, .snapshot-banner,
  .btn, .badge, .meter-track, .donut-center, footer {
    transition: background-color 0.4s var(--ease), color 0.4s var(--ease),
                border-color 0.4s var(--ease);
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  html, body {
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: var(--font);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-feature-settings: "ss01", "cv11";
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
    text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    line-height: 1.47;
  }

  body {
    background-image: var(--body-bg-image);
    min-height: 100vh;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* Subtle grain */
  body::before {
    content: '';
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 100;
    opacity: var(--grain-opacity);
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 400 400' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='n'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23n)'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
    mix-blend-mode: var(--grain-blend);
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1320px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: var(--space-12) var(--space-8) var(--space-24);
  }

  .snapshot-banner {
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 50;
    background: var(--banner-bg);
    backdrop-filter: blur(24px) saturate(180%);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(24px) saturate(180%);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 10px var(--space-8);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin: calc(var(--space-12) * -1) calc(var(--space-8) * -1) var(--space-12);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }
  .snapshot-banner-left {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }
  .snapshot-banner-left strong {
    color: var(--text);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .snapshot-banner-dot {
    width: 6px; height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--indigo);
    box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(94, 92, 230, 0.5);
  }
  .snapshot-banner-right {
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    font-style: italic;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-3);
  }
  .refresh-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    align-items: center;
  }
  .btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    padding: 6px 12px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    font-family: var(--font);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    color: var(--text);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.25s var(--ease);
    font-style: normal;
  }
  .btn:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }
  .btn:active { transform: translateY(0); }
  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--indigo);
    border-color: var(--indigo);
    color: white;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: #6e6cf0;
    border-color: #6e6cf0;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px -2px rgba(94, 92, 230, 0.4);
  }
  .btn-icon {
    width: 12px; height: 12px;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }
  .btn.copied {
    background: var(--green);
    border-color: var(--green);
    color: white;
  }

  /* Theme toggle — icon-only circular */
  .btn-icon-only {
    padding: 6px;
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: 50%;
    position: relative;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .btn-icon-only svg {
    width: 14px;
    height: 14px;
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(0deg) scale(1);
    transition: transform 0.4s var(--ease-spring), opacity 0.3s var(--ease);
  }
  /* Dark mode (default): show moon icon, hide sun */
  .btn-icon-only .theme-icon-sun {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(90deg) scale(0.6);
  }
  .btn-icon-only .theme-icon-moon {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(0deg) scale(1);
  }
  /* Light mode: show sun icon, hide moon */
  [data-theme="light"] .btn-icon-only .theme-icon-sun {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(0deg) scale(1);
  }
  [data-theme="light"] .btn-icon-only .theme-icon-moon {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(-90deg) scale(0.6);
  }
  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .snapshot-banner {
      margin: calc(var(--space-6) * -1) calc(var(--space-4) * -1) var(--space-8);
      padding: 8px var(--space-4);
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 4px;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
  }

  /* ——————————————————————— HERO ——————————————————————— */
  .hero {
    min-height: 62vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: var(--space-16) 0;
    position: relative;
  }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
    animation: fade-up 0.8s var(--ease) both;
  }
  .hero-eyebrow::before {
    content: '';
    width: 6px; height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--indigo);
    box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(94, 92, 230, 0.5);
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-size: clamp(56px, 8vw, 96px);
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 0.98;
    letter-spacing: -0.045em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
    background: var(--hero-title-gradient);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    animation: fade-up 0.9s 0.1s var(--ease) both;
  }

  .hero-title .accent {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--cyan) 0%, var(--indigo) 50%, var(--purple) 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-style: italic;
    display: block;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 680px;
    line-height: 1.4;
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
    animation: fade-up 1s 0.2s var(--ease) both;
  }

  .hero-meta {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-6);
    margin-top: var(--space-10);
    padding-top: var(--space-8);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    animation: fade-up 1.1s 0.35s var(--ease) both;
  }
  .hero-meta-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2px;
  }
  .hero-meta-label {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .hero-meta-value {
    font-size: var(--text-md);
    color: var(--text);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  @keyframes fade-up {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  /* ——————————————————————— SECTION HEADERS ——————————————————————— */
  .section {
    margin-top: var(--space-20);
  }
  .section-head {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }
  .section-num {
    font-size: 30px;
    color: var(--text);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-3);
  }

  /* ——————————————————————— TOOLTIP ——————————————————————— */
  .tt {
    position: relative;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 18px;
    height: 18px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
    background: var(--surface);
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-style: normal;
    letter-spacing: 0;
    cursor: help;
    text-transform: none;
    transition: all 0.2s var(--ease);
    vertical-align: middle;
  }
  .tt:hover {
    background: var(--surface-hover);
    color: var(--text);
    border-color: var(--border-strong);
  }
  .tt::after {
    content: attr(data-tip);
    position: absolute;
    bottom: calc(100% + 10px);
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(4px);
    width: max-content;
    max-width: 320px;
    padding: 10px 14px;
    background: var(--bg-elev-3);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.5;
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
    text-transform: none;
    text-align: left;
    white-space: normal;
    opacity: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    transition: opacity 0.2s var(--ease), transform 0.2s var(--ease);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px -8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
    z-index: 60;
  }
  .tt::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: calc(100% + 4px);
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    background: var(--bg-elev-3);
    border-right: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
    rotate: 45deg;
    opacity: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    transition: opacity 0.2s var(--ease);
    z-index: 60;
  }
  .tt:hover::after,
  .tt:focus::after {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0);
  }
  .tt:hover::before,
  .tt:focus::before {
    opacity: 1;
  }
  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .tt::after { max-width: 220px; font-size: var(--text-xs); }
  }
  .section-title {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    line-height: 1.4;
    max-width: 900px;
  }
  .section-title .muted {
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    font-weight: 400;
  }
  .section-lead {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    margin-top: var(--space-3);
    max-width: 720px;
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  /* ——————————————————————— KPI HERO GRID ——————————————————————— */
  .kpi-hero-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }
  .kpi-row-2 {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-4);
  }

  .card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    padding: var(--space-8);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: transform 0.4s var(--ease), background 0.3s var(--ease), border-color 0.3s var(--ease);
    backdrop-filter: blur(40px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(40px);
  }
  .card:hover {
    background: var(--surface-hover);
    border-color: var(--border-strong);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .card-eyebrow {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
  }

  .badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 5px;
    padding: 3px 10px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .badge-snapshot {
    background: rgba(94, 92, 230, 0.1);
    color: var(--indigo);
    border: 1px solid rgba(94, 92, 230, 0.2);
  }
  .badge-snapshot::before {
    content: '';
    width: 5px; height: 5px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--indigo);
  }
  .badge-pending {
    background: rgba(255, 159, 10, 0.1);
    color: var(--orange);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 159, 10, 0.18);
  }

  .kpi-hero {
    grid-row: span 1;
    padding: var(--space-10);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(10, 132, 255, 0.08), rgba(94, 92, 230, 0.04));
    border: 1px solid rgba(94, 92, 230, 0.2);
  }
  .kpi-hero .kpi-label {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }
  .kpi-hero .kpi-value {
    font-size: var(--text-hero);
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 0.95;
    letter-spacing: -0.05em;
    background: var(--kpi-hero-value-gradient);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  }
  .kpi-hero .kpi-unit {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-left: var(--space-2);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .kpi-hero .kpi-context {
    font-size: var(--text-md);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-top: var(--space-5);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .kpi-hero .kpi-context strong {
    color: var(--text);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .kpi {
    padding: var(--space-6);
  }
  .kpi-label {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }
  .kpi-value {
    font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -0.035em;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .kpi-value .unit {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-left: var(--space-2);
  }
  .kpi-delta {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-top: var(--space-3);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
  }
  .kpi-delta.good { color: var(--green); }
  .kpi-delta.warn { color: var(--orange); }
  .kpi-delta.bad { color: var(--red); }
  .kpi-delta-sub {
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  /* ——————————————————————— PIPELINE (hero visual) ——————————————————————— */
  .pipeline-card {
    padding: var(--space-12);
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02), transparent);
  }
  .pipeline-wrap {
    padding: var(--space-8) 0 var(--space-4);
    margin-top: var(--space-6);
  }
  .pipeline-track {
    position: relative;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 0;
    padding: var(--space-8) 0;
  }
  .pipeline-rail {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 12.5%;
    right: 12.5%;
    height: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg,
      rgba(255,255,255,0.15) 0%,
      var(--blue) 33%,
      var(--indigo) 66%,
      rgba(255,255,255,0.15) 100%);
    transform: translateY(-50%);
  }
  .pipeline-node {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    position: relative;
  }
  .pipeline-orb {
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: var(--text-md);
    font-weight: 600;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    transition: transform 0.4s var(--ease-spring);
  }
  .pipeline-orb::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: -8px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  }
  .pipeline-orb.biz {
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, rgba(255,255,255,0.15), rgba(255,255,255,0.05));
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
  }
  .pipeline-orb.recv {
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, var(--blue), #0062cc);
    color: white;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 28px -6px rgba(10, 132, 255, 0.5);
  }
  .pipeline-orb.review {
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, var(--indigo), #4340c4);
    color: white;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 28px -6px rgba(94, 92, 230, 0.5);
  }
  .pipeline-orb.ba {
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, rgba(191,90,242,0.2), rgba(191,90,242,0.08));
    color: var(--purple);
    border: 1px dashed rgba(191, 90, 242, 0.4);
  }
  .pipeline-node:hover .pipeline-orb {
    transform: scale(1.08);
  }
  .pipeline-label {
    margin-top: var(--space-4);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-weight: 500;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .pipeline-sublabel {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    margin-top: 2px;
  }
  .pipeline-gap {
    position: absolute;
    top: 100%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    margin-top: var(--space-6);
    text-align: center;
    width: 160px;
  }
  .pipeline-gap-value {
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .pipeline-gap-value.dim {
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
  }
  .pipeline-gap-label {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    margin-top: 4px;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  .pipeline-note {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    margin-top: var(--space-20);
    padding-top: var(--space-6);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    line-height: 1.55;
    max-width: 900px;
  }

  /* ——————————————————————— WORK TYPE ——————————————————————— */
  .worktype-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-4);
  }
  .worktype {
    padding: var(--space-6);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    transition: all 0.4s var(--ease);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .worktype::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: var(--wt-color, var(--blue));
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.3s var(--ease);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .worktype:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    border-color: var(--wt-color, var(--border-strong));
  }
  .worktype:hover::before {
    opacity: 0.04;
  }
  .worktype-head {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
  }
  .worktype-name {
    font-size: var(--text-md);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .worktype-dot {
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--wt-color, var(--blue));
    box-shadow: 0 0 12px var(--wt-glow, rgba(10, 132, 255, 0.4));
  }
  .worktype-value {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: var(--space-2);
  }
  .worktype-count {
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -0.035em;
  }
  .worktype-pct {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
  }
  .worktype-bar {
    margin-top: var(--space-4);
    height: 3px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    border-radius: 999px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .worktype-bar-fill {
    height: 100%;
    background: var(--wt-color, var(--blue));
    border-radius: 999px;
    transition: width 1.2s var(--ease);
    box-shadow: 0 0 12px var(--wt-glow, rgba(10, 132, 255, 0.3));
  }

  /* ——————————————————————— OUTCOME TRIO ——————————————————————— */
  .outcome-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    margin-top: var(--space-6);
  }
  .outcome {
    padding: var(--space-8);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .outcome-primary {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(48, 209, 88, 0.1), rgba(48, 209, 88, 0.02));
    border: 1px solid rgba(48, 209, 88, 0.2);
  }
  .outcome-secondary {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 159, 10, 0.08), transparent);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 159, 10, 0.18);
  }
  .outcome-label {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }
  .outcome-primary .outcome-label { color: var(--green); }
  .outcome-secondary .outcome-label { color: var(--orange); }
  .outcome-count-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }
  .outcome-count {
    font-size: var(--text-5xl);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .outcome-pct {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .outcome-desc {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.55;
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
  }

  /* ——————————————————————— TWO-COLUMN ——————————————————————— */
  .two-col {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.4fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    margin-top: var(--space-6);
  }
  .panel {
    padding: var(--space-8);
  }
  .panel-title {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }
  .panel-title em {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--cyan), var(--indigo));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  /* Bar chart */
  .bar-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 80px 1fr auto;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    padding: var(--space-3) 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .bar-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .bar-label {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }
  .bar-label .sub {
    display: block;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-top: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .bar-track {
    height: 24px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    border-radius: 6px;
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
  }
  .bar-fill {
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(94, 92, 230, 0.3), var(--indigo));
    border-radius: 6px;
    transition: width 1.2s var(--ease);
  }
  .bar-fill.current {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--orange), var(--pink));
    box-shadow: 0 0 16px -4px rgba(255, 159, 10, 0.5);
  }
  .bar-value {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--text);
    min-width: 32px;
    text-align: right;
  }

  /* Donut */
  .donut-wrap {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 160px 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-6);
    align-items: center;
  }
  .donut {
    width: 160px;
    height: 160px;
    position: relative;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .donut-center {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .donut-big {
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -0.035em;
  }
  .donut-small {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin-top: 4px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .legend {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-3);
  }
  .legend-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 10px 1fr auto;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-3);
  }
  .legend-dot {
    width: 10px; height: 10px;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }
  .legend-name {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .legend-val {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  /* ——————————————————————— SWEET SPOT ——————————————————————— */
  .hero-block {
    margin-top: var(--space-10);
    padding: var(--space-16);
    border-radius: var(--radius-2xl);
    background: var(--hero-block-bg);
    border: 1px solid rgba(94, 92, 230, 0.2);
    position: relative;
    /* Note: no overflow:hidden so zone tooltips can escape the card. */
  }
  .hero-block-eyebrow {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--indigo);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
  }
  .hero-block-title {
    font-size: clamp(28px, 3.5vw, 44px);
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.12;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    max-width: 900px;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .hero-block-title em {
    font-style: normal;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--orange), var(--pink));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .hero-block-body {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.55;
    margin-top: var(--space-6);
    max-width: 780px;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .meter-wrap {
    margin-top: var(--space-10);
    padding-top: var(--space-8);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 260px;
    gap: var(--space-8);
    align-items: center;
  }
  .meter-track {
    position: relative;
    height: 56px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    background:
      linear-gradient(90deg,
        rgba(255, 159, 10, 0.1) 0%,
        rgba(48, 209, 88, 0.1) 50%,
        rgba(255, 55, 95, 0.1) 100%);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    /* Note: no overflow:hidden so tooltips on zones can escape the track. */
  }
  .meter-zones {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
  }
  .meter-zone {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    font-weight: 500;
    border-right: 1px dashed rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  }
  .meter-zone:last-child { border-right: none; }
  .meter-zone-tt {
    position: relative;
    cursor: help;
    transition: color 0.2s var(--ease);
  }
  .meter-zone-tt:hover {
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .meter-zone-tt::after {
    content: attr(data-tip);
    position: absolute;
    bottom: calc(100% + 14px);
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(4px);
    width: max-content;
    max-width: 280px;
    padding: 10px 14px;
    background: var(--bg-elev-3);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.5;
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
    text-transform: none;
    text-align: left;
    white-space: normal;
    opacity: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    transition: opacity 0.2s var(--ease), transform 0.2s var(--ease);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px -8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
    z-index: 60;
  }
  .meter-zone-tt::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: calc(100% + 8px);
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    background: var(--bg-elev-3);
    border-right: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
    rotate: 45deg;
    opacity: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    transition: opacity 0.2s var(--ease);
    z-index: 60;
  }
  .meter-zone-tt:hover::after,
  .meter-zone-tt:focus::after {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0);
  }
  .meter-zone-tt:hover::before,
  .meter-zone-tt:focus::before {
    opacity: 1;
  }
  .meter-pin {
    position: absolute;
    top: -4px; bottom: -4px;
    width: 4px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--orange), var(--pink));
    border-radius: 999px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 159, 10, 0.6), 0 0 4px var(--pink);
  }
  .meter-pin::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    width: 16px;
    height: 16px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--orange), var(--pink));
    box-shadow: 0 0 24px rgba(255, 159, 10, 0.8);
  }
  .meter-pin::after {
    content: 'NOW';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -24px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--orange);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  }
  .meter-call {
    font-size: var(--text-md);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.5;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .meter-call strong {
    color: var(--text);
    font-weight: 600;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  /* ——————————————————————— PM CARDS ——————————————————————— */
  .person-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-4);
    margin-top: var(--space-6);
  }
  .person-card {
    padding: var(--space-8);
    position: relative;
  }
  .person-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }
  .person-avatar {
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .person-avatar.mar {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--cyan), var(--indigo));
    color: white;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px -8px rgba(100, 210, 255, 0.4);
  }
  .person-avatar.david {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--purple), var(--pink));
    color: white;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px -8px rgba(191, 90, 242, 0.4);
  }
  .person-info {
    flex: 1;
  }
  .person-name {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }
  .person-role {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    margin-top: 2px;
  }
  .person-stat {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    padding: var(--space-4) 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
  }
  .person-stat-value {
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.035em;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .person-stat-label {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
  }
  .alloc-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 90px 1fr 40px;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }
  .alloc-name {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .alloc-track {
    height: 6px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    border-radius: 999px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .alloc-fill {
    height: 100%;
    border-radius: 999px;
    transition: width 1.4s var(--ease);
  }
  .alloc-fill.intake { background: var(--purple); }
  .alloc-fill.triage { background: var(--orange); }
  .alloc-fill.project { background: var(--blue); }
  .alloc-fill.comms { background: var(--green); }
  .alloc-pct {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 500;
    text-align: right;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .person-note {
    margin-top: var(--space-6);
    padding-top: var(--space-5);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    line-height: 1.5;
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
  }

  /* ——————————————————————— RECOMMENDATIONS ——————————————————————— */
  .recs {
    padding: var(--space-12);
    border-radius: var(--radius-2xl);
    background:
      linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.02), transparent),
      var(--bg-elev-1);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin-top: var(--space-6);
  }
  .rec-item {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 72px 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-6);
    padding: var(--space-6) 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .rec-item:first-child { padding-top: 0; }
  .rec-item:last-child { padding-bottom: 0; border-bottom: none; }
  .rec-num {
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--indigo);
    font-feature-settings: "ss01";
  }
  .rec-content h4 {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text);
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }
  .rec-content p {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.55;
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
  }
  .rec-content em {
    color: var(--text);
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* ——————————————————————— FOOTER ——————————————————————— */
  footer {
    margin-top: var(--space-24);
    padding-top: var(--space-6);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--space-4);
  }

  /* ——————————————————————— TIMELINE ——————————————————————— */
  .timeline-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-4);
    margin-top: var(--space-6);
  }
  .timeline-card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    padding: var(--space-6) var(--space-6) var(--space-8);
    transition: all 0.4s var(--ease);
    backdrop-filter: blur(40px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(40px);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .timeline-card:hover {
    background: var(--surface-hover);
    border-color: var(--border-strong);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
  .timeline-current {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(94, 92, 230, 0.12), rgba(10, 132, 255, 0.04));
    border: 1px solid rgba(94, 92, 230, 0.3);
    box-shadow: 0 0 40px -12px rgba(94, 92, 230, 0.3);
  }
  .timeline-current::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--cyan), var(--indigo), var(--purple));
  }
  .timeline-empty {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.015);
    border: 1px dashed rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
  }
  .timeline-span-2 {
    grid-column: span 2;
  }
  .timeline-eyebrow {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .timeline-current .timeline-eyebrow { color: var(--indigo); }
  .timeline-dot {
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--text-quaternary);
  }
  .timeline-dot.active {
    background: var(--indigo);
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(94, 92, 230, 0.8);
    animation: pulse-timeline 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  .timeline-dot.dim {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
  }
  @keyframes pulse-timeline {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
    50% { opacity: 0.4; }
  }
  .timeline-window {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
  }
  .timeline-primary {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    padding: var(--space-3) 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .timeline-value {
    font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .timeline-current .timeline-value {
    background: var(--hero-title-gradient);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  }
  .timeline-value.tl-zero {
    color: var(--text-quaternary);
  }
  .timeline-unit {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
  }
  .timeline-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-3);
    margin-top: var(--space-2);
  }
  .timeline-span-2 .timeline-stats {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  }
  .tl-stat {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2px;
  }
  .tl-stat-value {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .tl-stat-value.tl-muted {
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: var(--text-md);
  }
  .tl-stat-suffix {
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-left: 2px;
    letter-spacing: 0;
  }
  .tl-stat-label {
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .timeline-note {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-top: var(--space-2);
  }
  .timeline-empty-note {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    line-height: 1.55;
    margin-top: var(--space-3);
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
  }
  .timeline-span-2 .timeline-primary {
    padding: var(--space-4) 0;
  }
  .timeline-span-2 .timeline-value {
    font-size: var(--text-5xl);
  }

  /* ——————————————————————— RESPONSIVE ——————————————————————— */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .kpi-hero-grid, .kpi-row-2, .worktype-grid, .outcome-grid, .two-col, .person-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
    .kpi-hero { grid-column: span 2; }
    .outcome-grid > :first-child { grid-column: span 2; }
    .timeline-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .timeline-span-2 { grid-column: span 2; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .container { padding: var(--space-6) var(--space-4) var(--space-16); }
    .kpi-hero-grid, .kpi-row-2, .worktype-grid, .outcome-grid, .two-col, .person-grid, .timeline-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .kpi-hero { grid-column: span 1; }
    .outcome-grid > :first-child { grid-column: span 1; }
    .timeline-span-2 { grid-column: span 1; }
    .hero-meta { flex-wrap: wrap; gap: var(--space-4); }
    .pipeline-card { padding: var(--space-6); }
    .pipeline-orb { width: 44px; height: 44px; }
    .pipeline-gap-value { font-size: var(--text-xl); }
    .meter-wrap { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .donut-wrap { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .rec-item { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: var(--space-3); }
    .recs { padding: var(--space-8); }
  }

  /* Reveal */
  .reveal {
    animation: fade-up 0.8s var(--ease) both;
  }
  .card, .worktype, .outcome, .person-card {
    animation: fade-up 0.8s var(--ease) both;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">

    <!-- ══════════ SNAPSHOT BANNER (sticky) ══════════ -->
    <div class="snapshot-banner">
      <div class="snapshot-banner-left">
        <span class="snapshot-banner-dot"></span>
        <span><strong>Snapshot</strong> · taken <span data-snapshot-time="full">{{ snapshot_timestamp }}</span></span>
      </div>
      <div class="snapshot-banner-right">
        <div class="refresh-actions">
          <button class="btn btn-icon-only" onclick="toggleTheme()" aria-label="Toggle theme" title="Switch light/dark">
            <svg class="theme-icon-sun" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="4"/><path d="M12 2v2M12 20v2M4.93 4.93l1.41 1.41M17.66 17.66l1.41 1.41M2 12h2M20 12h2M4.93 19.07l1.41-1.41M17.66 6.34l1.41-1.41"/></svg>
            <svg class="theme-icon-moon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 12.79A9 9 0 1 1 11.21 3 7 7 0 0 0 21 12.79z"/></svg>
          </button>
          <a href="https://app.asana.com/0/portfolio/1214057614427291/list" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn">
            <svg class="btn-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"/><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"/><line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"/></svg>
            View live in Asana
          </a>
          <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="triggerRefresh(this)" id="refresh-btn">
            <svg class="btn-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="23 4 23 10 17 10"/><polyline points="1 20 1 14 7 14"/><path d="M3.51 9a9 9 0 0 1 14.85-3.36L23 10M1 14l4.64 4.36A9 9 0 0 0 20.49 15"/></svg>
            <span class="btn-label">Refresh data</span>
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ══════════ HERO ══════════ -->
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-eyebrow"><span data-snapshot-time="eyebrow">{{ snapshot_eyebrow }}</span></div>
      <h1 class="hero-title">
        The CoE, in numbers.
        <span class="accent">Quietly working.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        {{ hero_total_spelled }} requests. A {{ hero_cycle_bd }} business-day review cycle. {{ hero_gate_pct_spelled }} percent filtered at the gate. Here's what's actually moving — and what still needs to be measured before the resource conversation.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-meta">
        <div class="hero-meta-item">
          <span class="hero-meta-label">Snapshot taken</span>
          <span class="hero-meta-value" data-snapshot-time="full">{{ snapshot_timestamp }}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-meta-item">
          <span class="hero-meta-label">Source</span>
          <span class="hero-meta-value">Asana · CoE Portfolio</span>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-meta-item">
          <span class="hero-meta-label">Refresh</span>
          <span class="hero-meta-value">Auto · Mon–Fri 12 PM ET</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ══════════ §01 KPIs ══════════ -->
    <section class="section">
      <div class="section-head">
        <div class="section-num">01 · Overview<span class="tt" tabindex="0" data-tip="The headline numbers — the eight KPIs executives see first. Review cycle time, open backlog, BA handoff status, weekly intake, escalations, delivered work, and triage coverage.">i</span></div>
        <h2 class="section-title">
          The headline numbers.
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="kpi-hero-grid">
        <!-- Hero KPI -->
        <div class="card kpi-hero">
          <div class="card-eyebrow">
            Headline · service level
            <span class="badge badge-snapshot">Snapshot</span>
          </div>
          <div class="kpi-label">Average · received → first review</div>
          <div class="kpi-value">{{ kpi_review_avg }}<span class="kpi-unit">business days</span></div>
          <div class="kpi-context">
            Across <strong>{{ kpi_review_substantive_count }} substantive reviews</strong> — items that required real CoE analysis, excluding requests marked <em>Already Completed</em> or <em>Not Needed</em>. Median <strong>{{ kpi_review_median }} bd</strong>, tight range {{ kpi_review_range_low }}–{{ kpi_review_range_high }}.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card kpi">
          <div class="card-eyebrow">
            Active backlog
            <span class="badge badge-snapshot">Snapshot</span>
          </div>
          <div class="kpi-label">Open requests</div>
          <div class="kpi-value">{{ kpi_backlog_open }}<span class="unit">of {{ kpi_backlog_total }}</span></div>
          <div class="kpi-delta warn">↗ Trending up<span class="kpi-delta-sub"> · {{ kpi_backlog_real_work }} need real work</span></div>
        </div>

        <div class="card kpi">
          <div class="card-eyebrow">
            Cycle · review → BA
            {% if kpi_ba_count > 0 %}<span class="badge badge-snapshot">Snapshot</span>{% else %}<span class="badge badge-pending">Pending</span>{% endif %}
          </div>
          <div class="kpi-label">Average business days</div>
          <div class="kpi-value">{{ kpi_ba_avg }}<span class="unit">{% if kpi_ba_avg != "—" %}bd{% else %}d{% endif %}</span></div>
          <div class="kpi-delta"><span class="kpi-delta-sub">{{ kpi_ba_pending_total }} BA dates set</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="kpi-row-2">
        <div class="card kpi">
          <div class="card-eyebrow">Intakes · W{{ kpi_w_current }}<span class="badge badge-snapshot">Snapshot</span></div>
          <div class="kpi-label">New this week <span style="text-transform: none; letter-spacing: 0; font-weight: 400; color: var(--text-quaternary);">· {{ tw_window_label }}</span></div>
          <div class="kpi-value">{{ kpi_w_current_intakes }}<span class="unit">new</span></div>
          <div class="kpi-delta"><span class="kpi-delta-sub">vs. {{ kpi_w_minus1_intakes }} in W{{ kpi_w_minus1 }}</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="card kpi">
          <div class="card-eyebrow">Escalated / rejected<span class="badge badge-snapshot">Snapshot</span></div>
          <div class="kpi-label">This cycle</div>
          <div class="kpi-value">{{ kpi_escalated }}<span class="unit">proj</span></div>
          <div class="kpi-delta"><span class="kpi-delta-sub">{{ kpi_escalated_pct }} filtered at gate</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="card kpi">
          <div class="card-eyebrow">Delivered<span class="badge badge-snapshot">Snapshot</span></div>
          <div class="kpi-label">Completed work · last cycle</div>
          <div class="kpi-value">{{ kpi_delivered }}<span class="unit">done</span></div>
          <div class="kpi-delta warn">First delivery pending · Sprint 10</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card kpi">
          <div class="card-eyebrow">Priority set<span class="badge badge-snapshot">Snapshot</span></div>
          <div class="kpi-label">Triaged</div>
          <div class="kpi-value">{{ kpi_priority_set }}<span class="unit">/{{ kpi_priority_total }}</span></div>
          <div class="kpi-delta"><span class="kpi-delta-sub">{{ kpi_priority_unset }} untriaged for priority</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ══════════ §02 Timeline ══════════ -->
    <section class="section">
      <div class="section-head">
        <div class="section-num">02 · Timeline<span class="tt" tabindex="0" data-tip="Five time windows: this week, last week, this month, last month, and a rolling six-month view. Lets leaders see cadence and direction — is the CoE accelerating, steady, or slowing down?">i</span></div>
        <h2 class="section-title">
          Five windows, <span class="muted">honest about where the CoE was born.</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="section-lead">
          The CoE received its first intake on {{ coe_start_display }}. Periods before that show zero activity — not because the firm wasn't logging requests, but because the CoE didn't yet exist to process them.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline-grid">
        <div class="timeline-card timeline-current">
          <div class="timeline-eyebrow">
            <span class="timeline-dot active"></span>
            This week · W{{ timeline_w_current }}
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-window">{{ tw_window_label }}</div>
          <div class="timeline-primary">
            <span class="timeline-value">{{ timeline_w_current_intakes }}</span>
            <span class="timeline-unit">new intakes</span>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-stats">
            <div class="tl-stat">
              <span class="tl-stat-value">{{ timeline_w_current_reviews }}</span>
              <span class="tl-stat-label">reviews completed</span>
            </div>
            <div class="tl-stat">
              <span class="tl-stat-value">{{ timeline_w_current_cycle }}{% if timeline_w_current_cycle != "—" %}<span class="tl-stat-suffix">bd</span>{% endif %}</span>
              <span class="tl-stat-label">avg cycle</span>
            </div>
            <div class="tl-stat">
              <span class="tl-stat-value">{{ timeline_w_current_gate }}</span>
              <span class="tl-stat-label">closed at gate</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-card">
          <div class="timeline-eyebrow">
            <span class="timeline-dot"></span>
            Last week · W{{ timeline_w_minus1 }}
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-window">{{ lw_window_label }}</div>
          <div class="timeline-primary">
            <span class="timeline-value">{{ timeline_w_minus1_intakes }}</span>
            <span class="timeline-unit">intakes</span>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-stats">
            <div class="tl-stat">
              <span class="tl-stat-value">{{ timeline_w_minus1_reviews }}</span>
              <span class="tl-stat-label">reviews</span>
            </div>
            <div class="tl-stat">
              <span class="tl-stat-value">{{ timeline_w_minus1_cycle }}{% if timeline_w_minus1_cycle != "—" %}<span class="tl-stat-suffix">bd</span>{% endif %}</span>
              <span class="tl-stat-label">avg cycle</span>
            </div>
            <div class="tl-stat">
              {% if timeline_w_minus1_has_reviews %}
              <span class="tl-stat-value">{{ timeline_w_minus1_reviews }}</span>
              <span class="tl-stat-label">reviewed</span>
              {% else %}
              <span class="tl-stat-value tl-muted">seeding</span>
              <span class="tl-stat-label">week</span>
              {% endif %}
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-card">
          <div class="timeline-eyebrow">
            <span class="timeline-dot"></span>
            This month · {{ tm_month_name }}
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-window">{{ tm_window_label }}</div>
          <div class="timeline-primary">
            <span class="timeline-value">{{ timeline_month_intakes }}</span>
            <span class="timeline-unit">intakes</span>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-stats">
            <div class="tl-stat">
              <span class="tl-stat-value">{{ timeline_month_reviewed }}</span>
              <span class="tl-stat-label">reviewed</span>
            </div>
            <div class="tl-stat">
              <span class="tl-stat-value">{{ timeline_month_avg_cycle }}{% if timeline_month_avg_cycle != "—" %}<span class="tl-stat-suffix">bd</span>{% endif %}</span>
              <span class="tl-stat-label">avg cycle</span>
            </div>
            <div class="tl-stat">
              <span class="tl-stat-value">{{ timeline_month_escalated }}</span>
              <span class="tl-stat-label">escalated</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        {% if timeline_lm_has_coe %}
        <div class="timeline-card">
          <div class="timeline-eyebrow">
            <span class="timeline-dot"></span>
            Last month · {{ lm_month_name }}
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-window">{{ lm_window_label }}</div>
          <div class="timeline-primary">
            <span class="timeline-value">{{ timeline_lm_intakes }}</span>
            <span class="timeline-unit">intakes</span>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-stats">
            <div class="tl-stat">
              <span class="tl-stat-value">{{ timeline_lm_reviews }}</span>
              <span class="tl-stat-label">reviewed</span>
            </div>
            <div class="tl-stat">
              <span class="tl-stat-value">{{ timeline_lm_avg_cycle }}{% if timeline_lm_avg_cycle != "—" %}<span class="tl-stat-suffix">bd</span>{% endif %}</span>
              <span class="tl-stat-label">avg cycle</span>
            </div>
            <div class="tl-stat">
              <span class="tl-stat-value">{{ timeline_lm_escalated }}</span>
              <span class="tl-stat-label">escalated</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        {% else %}
        <div class="timeline-card timeline-empty">
          <div class="timeline-eyebrow">
            <span class="timeline-dot dim"></span>
            Last month · {{ lm_month_name }}
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-window">{{ lm_window_label }}</div>
          <div class="timeline-primary">
            <span class="timeline-value tl-zero">{{ timeline_lm_intakes }}</span>
            <span class="timeline-unit">intakes</span>
          </div>
          <p class="timeline-empty-note">
            CoE did not yet exist to receive requests. The business was logging intakes into the EPMO portfolio, which the CoE inherited on {{ coe_start_display }}.
          </p>
        </div>
        {% endif %}

        <div class="timeline-card timeline-empty timeline-span-2">
          <div class="timeline-eyebrow">
            <span class="timeline-dot dim"></span>
            Last 6 months · {{ six_mo_window_label }}
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-window">182-day window</div>
          <div class="timeline-primary">
            <span class="timeline-value">{{ timeline_6mo_intakes }}</span>
            <span class="timeline-unit">intakes · all in the last {{ timeline_6mo_days_active }} days</span>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-stats">
            <div class="tl-stat">
              <span class="tl-stat-value">{{ timeline_6mo_days_pre_coe }}</span>
              <span class="tl-stat-label">days pre-CoE</span>
            </div>
            <div class="tl-stat">
              <span class="tl-stat-value">{{ timeline_6mo_days_active }}</span>
              <span class="tl-stat-label">days CoE active</span>
            </div>
            <div class="tl-stat">
              <span class="tl-stat-value">{{ timeline_6mo_avg_cycle }}<span class="tl-stat-suffix">bd</span></span>
              <span class="tl-stat-label">avg cycle</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="timeline-note">
            The {{ timeline_6mo_days_pre_coe }}-day pre-CoE period is when these requests lived in the business's EPMO portfolio with no governance. The {{ timeline_6mo_days_active }} days of CoE activity processed {{ timeline_6mo_reviews }} reviews{% if timeline_6mo_avg_cycle != "—" %} at an average of {{ timeline_6mo_avg_cycle }} bd each — the first measurable proof of the "faster than previous state" claim{% endif %}.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ══════════ §03 Pipeline ══════════ -->
    <section class="section">
      <div class="section-head">
        <div class="section-num">03 · Pipeline<span class="tt" tabindex="0" data-tip="The end-to-end journey of a request: Business created → CoE received → First review → BA assigned. Each gap shown in business days so you can spot where work waits.">i</span></div>
        <h2 class="section-title">
          End to end, in one glance. <span class="muted">Once we have it, we move in four.</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="section-lead">
          All durations measured in <em style="color: var(--text); font-style: normal; font-weight: 500;">business days</em> — weekends excluded throughout. <em style="color: var(--text); font-style: normal; font-weight: 500;">Seeding</em> refers to legacy requests inherited from the EPMO portfolio when the CoE began operating — they show artificially long upstream times because they existed before the CoE could receive them.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card pipeline-card">
        <div class="pipeline-wrap">
          <div class="pipeline-track">
            <div class="pipeline-rail"></div>
            <div class="pipeline-node">
              <div class="pipeline-orb biz">①</div>
              <div class="pipeline-label">Business created</div>
              <div class="pipeline-sublabel">in EPMO portfolio</div>
            </div>
            <div class="pipeline-node">
              <div class="pipeline-orb recv">②</div>
              <div class="pipeline-label">CoE received</div>
              <div class="pipeline-sublabel">Received Date</div>
              <div class="pipeline-gap" style="left: 0; transform: translateX(-50%);">
                <div class="pipeline-gap-value">{{ pipeline_upstream_bd }}<span style="font-size:16px; color:var(--text-tertiary); margin-left:3px;">bd</span></div>
                <div class="pipeline-gap-label">Upstream · seeding</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="pipeline-node">
              <div class="pipeline-orb review">③</div>
              <div class="pipeline-label">First review</div>
              <div class="pipeline-sublabel">First Review Date</div>
              <div class="pipeline-gap" style="left: 0; transform: translateX(-50%);">
                <div class="pipeline-gap-value" style="color: var(--cyan);">{{ pipeline_review_bd }}<span style="font-size:16px; color:var(--text-tertiary); margin-left:3px;">bd</span></div>
                <div class="pipeline-gap-label">CoE review time</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="pipeline-node">
              <div class="pipeline-orb ba">④</div>
              <div class="pipeline-label"{% if kpi_ba_count == 0 %} style="color: var(--text-tertiary);"{% endif %}>BA assigned</div>
